public class MinExtensionSet<NodeType,EdgeType>
extends MinExtension<NodeType,EdgeType>

Stores and sorts the created extensions during the test for being canonical.

It represents the head marker of a double linked ring list.

Author:
Marc Woerlein (woerlein@informatik.uni-erlangen.de)
